name: Statues 02 | VENUS
description:
Part of a collection for a study about narrative, composition, and light.
"Venus is the first experiment, I try to show her feeling after Apollo reveal to Vulcan (her husband) the relationship with her lover Mars, and be abandoned by Mars after the revelation"
You can see the full project, with some tests on Behance.net/animabob

Collection: STATUES (02 of 03)
